{"title":"Xtracycle Packs the Hopper Cargo eBike with a 500lb Carrying Capacity","link":"https://bikerumor.com/xtracycle-hopper-cargo-ebike/","date":1726833600000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" alt=\"(Photos / Xtracycle)\" /></p>\n<p>Cargo bikes &amp; cargo bike conversions have been <a href=\"https://xtracycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Xtracycle</a>‘s jam for 25 years. Just recently, they announced the newest member of their cargo family, the <a href=\"https://xtracycle.com/products/hopper-compact-cargo?variant=47648147865896\" target=\"_blank\">Hopper</a>. Xtracycle said they designed the Hopper to be the most intuitive, compact family cargo bike on the market. Let’s check it out.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-full-side-jpeg-e1726682111984.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"875\" height=\"511\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-full-side-jpeg-e1726682111984.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike full side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-full-side-jpeg-e1726682111984.webp 875w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-full-side-jpeg-e1726682111984-297x173.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-full-side-jpeg-e1726682111984-120x70.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-full-side-jpeg-e1726682111984-768x449.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Xtracycle)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Hopper has a shorter wheelbase, so it rides closer to a regular bicycle. Plus, it can fit riders from 5′ to 6’5″. And even though it’s on the smaller size it can still haul a claimed 500lbs (we’re assuming this includes passengers).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Front-side-jpeg-e1726682148832.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"840\" height=\"598\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Front-side-jpeg-e1726682148832.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike Front side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Front-side-jpeg-e1726682148832.webp 840w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Front-side-jpeg-e1726682148832-297x211.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Front-side-jpeg-e1726682148832-120x85.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Front-side-jpeg-e1726682148832-768x547.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Steve Zourntos, who’s the Head of Product over at Xtracycle says that they’ve “taken everything [they’ve] learned about cargo bikes and wrapped it up in this nimble, easy-to-use package.” He added that the Hopper is ideal for school drop-offs, errands, and commuting. It can even park vertically, making it the “perfect solution for urban family”.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike haulin' kids\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-jpeg.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-haulin-kids-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike playground\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-jpeg.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-playground-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the first eBike for Xtracycle that comes equipped with a throttle. Plus, it comes with Hooptie passenger bars, a front PorterRack, full-coverage fenders, integrated lights, and a beefy center kickstand. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-suspension-fork-jpg-e1726682225157.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"921\" height=\"601\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-suspension-fork-jpg-e1726682225157.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike suspension fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-suspension-fork-jpg-e1726682225157.webp 921w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-suspension-fork-jpg-e1726682225157-297x194.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-suspension-fork-jpg-e1726682225157-120x78.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-suspension-fork-jpg-e1726682225157-768x501.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-beefy-kickstand-jpg-e1726682241751.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-beefy-kickstand-jpg-e1726682241751.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike beefy kickstand\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-beefy-kickstand-jpg-e1726682241751.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-beefy-kickstand-jpg-e1726682241751-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-beefy-kickstand-jpg-e1726682241751-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-beefy-kickstand-jpg-e1726682241751-768x432.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-PorterRack-jpg-e1726682269545.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"591\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-PorterRack-jpg-e1726682269545.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike PorterRack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-PorterRack-jpg-e1726682269545.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-PorterRack-jpg-e1726682269545-297x176.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-PorterRack-jpg-e1726682269545-120x71.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-PorterRack-jpg-e1726682269545-768x454.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Hooptie-Bars-jpg-e1726682284892.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"603\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Hooptie-Bars-jpg-e1726682284892.webp\" alt=\"Xtracycle's new Hooper Cargo eBike Hooptie Bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Hooptie-Bars-jpg-e1726682284892.webp 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Hooptie-Bars-jpg-e1726682284892-297x179.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Hooptie-Bars-jpg-e1726682284892-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Xtracycles-new-Hooper-Cargo-eBike-Hooptie-Bars-jpg-e1726682284892-768x463.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Hopper Key Retail and Features</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $2999 (introductory price of $2499 from October 11th through the 13th)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>750W rear hub motor </li>\n\n\n\n<li>720 Watt hour battery</li>\n\n\n\n<li>torque sensor assists up to 28 mph </li>\n\n\n\n<li>20” wheels</li>\n\n\n\n<li>60 miles on a single charge</li>\n\n\n\n<li>hydraulic disc brakes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>front suspension fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>suspension-dropper post</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The Hopper is available for pre-order at the link below. It will be shipping nationwide on October 11th. The Hopper will be available for purchase at the introductory price of $2499 until October 13th. These prices include free shipping and local assembly where available. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://xtracycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Xtracycle.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/xtracycle-hopper-cargo-ebike/\">Xtracycle Packs the Hopper Cargo eBike with a 500lb Carrying Capacity</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"963d6c1fa2bed532f8239686d17e6cdbebee41df4bbd57f5cc0b16dcea67f272","category":"Cycling"}